.TH PKGORPHAN 1 "PKGMAINT-#VERSION# Manual"

.SH NAME
pkgorhpan \- list orphaned packages on your system

.SH SYNOPSIS
.PP
.B pkgorphan

.SH DESCRIPTION
\fIpkgorphan\fR script lists installed packages which are not present in
the \fIpkgsrcdir\fR directories, configured in \fB/etc/pkgman.conf\fR.
.PP
This script requires \fBpkgman\fR(8).
